songs.title: Beautiful
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Now when I step up in the place, I know my freshness is no disgrace
I'm winning this race against you losers
I'm not new but what's it to ya?
I'ma do me so you can do ya
Early in the morning, you can hear the rooster
Yeah, I said I'm wide awake now
Tryna see ya gravity now
Maybe I could just hide away now
Hopefully have a home place to lay down
Super hard, gotta get my cake now
Making nice songs, mixtape I have to take now
Songs hotter than the sun, I'm the shade now
Speechless homies got nothing to say now
Nothing to say now
Nothing to say now, I'ma get famous any day now
Y'all gon' like "Andre, this ain't 'Hey, now?'"
And I'ma be like "I'm getting paid now"
I know how dumb this may sound
But the hating heads is gonna have to pay now
Yeah, the hating heads is gonna have to pay now
Yeah, is gonna have to pay now
Yeah
